        "timestamp": "2019-12-30 06:32:04.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(3 comments)\n\nI don't think we need to modify ServiceInfo model across all the tests, just to add a single field on a single test.\n\nMoreover, in the test that use the field - the test of object is ignored, so even more unnecessary, as I see it.\n\nAnd moreover, you're assuming all the summary of all tests is null, which is either wrong or a defect: the summary should contain the request's summary when TEMPLATES toggle is on.",
